To compile this program, you will need the sqlite3 (libsqlite3-dev), FUSE (libfuse-dev), and glib (libglib2.0-dev) development files.

If you run into problems with TagFS, try running TagFS in single-thread mode. This may help solve the problem. If not, it will still make it easier to identify the problem in the logs. This is accomplished with the -s flag. Example: ./tagfs -s TagFS/